## 📋 Description

**Emonado** is a comprehensive web-based mental health management platform that bridges the gap between patients and psychologists. It provides an integrated digital ecosystem where patients can track their mental well-being, book appointments, maintain personal journals, and benefit from AI-powered emotional analysis — while psychologists get powerful tools to manage consultations, monitor patient progress, and generate reports.

### 🎯 Purpose & Goals

- Digitise and streamline the psychologist–patient relationship
- Empower patients with self-care tools: mood journals, adaptive tests, and chatbot support
- Equip psychologists with dashboards, dossiers, PDF exports, and predictive insights
- Leverage AI (Google Gemini, OpenAI, Groq) for emotional analysis and coaching suggestions
- Provide administrators with full user, questionnaire, and audit-log management

### 👥 Target Users

| Role | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Patient** | Books appointments, writes journals, completes psychological tests, chats with the AI assistant |
| **Psychologue** | Manages consultations, reviews patient dossiers, prepares sessions, exports PDF reports |
| **Admin** | Manages users, questionnaires, appointment types, and monitors system audit logs |

### ✨ Main Features

- 📅 **Appointment Management** — Patients book, psychologists confirm/cancel; interactive calendar view
- 📓 **Mood Journal** — Rich journal entries with mood tagging, voice transcription, and music therapy recommendations
- 🤖 **AI Chatbot** — Gemini-powered chatbot for patient support and mental health coaching
- 📊 **Emotional Analysis** — AI-driven emotion recognition and insight reporting
- 🧩 **Adaptive Psychological Tests** — Branching questionnaires that adjust to patient responses
- 🎭 **Children's Space** — Illustrated story-based psychological scenes for child assessments
- 🗂️ **Medical Dossiers** — Full patient records: consultations, prescriptions, documents
- 📄 **PDF Reports** — Export dossiers, journal summaries, and consultation reports (via KnpSnappy/DomPDF)
- 💬 **Real-time Messaging** — Patient–psychologist messaging with Mercure (SSE)
- 📱 **SMS Reminders** — Appointment reminders sent via Mailjet SMS API
- 🛡️ **Role-Based Access Control** — Separate interfaces and permissions for each role
- 🔍 **Audit Logging** — Tracked login and action history for administrators

