## ✅ Prerequisites

Before running the project, ensure the following are installed on your machine:

- **PHP** ≥ 8.1 with extensions: `ctype`, `iconv`, `mbstring`, `pdo_mysql`, `xml`, `intl`
- **Composer** (latest stable)
- **MySQL** or **MariaDB** (or Docker + Docker Compose for the containerised DB)
- **Node.js** ≥ 18 & **npm** (for front-end assets, if needed)
- **Symfony CLI** (optional but recommended)
- **wkhtmltopdf** (required for PDF export) — [Download](https://wkhtmltopdf.org/downloads.html)

